URL:-https://www.ndtv.com/business/car-sales-auto-sales-news-passenger-car-sales-fall-nearly-24-percent-in-september-industry-body-siam-2115129



TITLE:
Passenger Vehicle Sales Fall Nearly 24% In September: Industry Body SIAM


Content:
Auto sales news: Passenger car sales fell 33.40% to 1,31,281 units last month, SIAM data showedContent:
Get Breaking news, live coverage, and Latest News from India and around the world on NDTV.com. Catch all the Live TV action on NDTV 24x7 and NDTV India. Like us on Facebook or follow us on Twitter and Instagram for latest news and live news updates.Content:
